591
00:50:31,660 --> 00:50:33,173
Jeremy Snyder, Cheyenne, Wyoming.

592
00:50:33,420 --> 00:50:34,409
Sargento Weaver.

593
00:50:34,620 --> 00:50:36,372
- De onde vem?
- Colombus, Georgia.

